Package com.exclamationlabs.connid.base.connector.authenticator.model

Class OAuth2AccessTokenContainer

java.lang.Object
com.exclamationlabs.connid.base.connector.authenticator.model.OAuth2AccessTokenContainer
public class OAuth2AccessTokenContainer
extends java.lang.Object
Model holding possible OAuth2 response data. Not all fields may be populated from response, but accessToken should be expected to have a value from an OAuth2 response.
